UBcai", "last_touched": 1624004809, "title": "苹果笔记本售后因没发票被拒，怎么办，可以用别人的发票吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/784051", "created": 1623930449, "content": "坐标武汉，没有直营店，只有授权服务点。\r\n闲鱼买了个带 AC+的 MacBookPro，但是没发票也没 AC 购买凭证。\r\n最近发现屏幕涂层脱落 想着这个保修 4 年，联系官网后就去服务点了，但服务点表示没有发票不给安排维修。\r\n\r\n发票这个东西能用别人的吗？ 这个应该没有记录序列号吧？", "content_rendered": "<p>坐标武汉，没有直营店，只有授权服务点。\n闲鱼买了个带 AC+的 MacBookPro，但是没发票也没 AC 购买凭证。\n最近发现屏幕涂层脱落 想着这个保修 4 年，联系官网后就去服务点了，但服务点表示没有发票不给安排维修。</p>\n<p>发票这个东西能用别人的吗？ 这个应该没有记录序列号吧？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1623930449, "replies": 53, "id": 784051}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1620106980", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1620106980", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 6215, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980", "stars": 5545, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "elone", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/14e9/6802/176010_mini.png?m=1499605313", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/elone", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1465052347, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/14e9/6802/176010_mini.png?m=1499605313", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/14e9/6802/176010_mini.png?m=1499605313", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 176010}, "last_reply_by": "trysingtime", "last_touched": 1624006919, "title": "一大早 deepin 崩溃，准备把开发环境切换回 win10 了。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/784199", "created": 1623990049, "content": "用 deepin 也用了一两年了，平时感觉还好，虽然小 bug 有点多。\r\n\r\n今天早上用着正常，合上盖子带来单位上班，突然发现无线鼠标不能用了，触摸板也不能用了。想着难道触摸板被关了？想打开控制中心看看，控制中心也打不开了。\r\n\r\n奇怪的是，有线鼠标还能用。\r\n\r\n突然就很想把开发环境切回 win10 了，不知道现在 wsl2 做开发怎么样，主要是 web 开发，flutter 开发。", "content_rendered": "<p>用 deepin 也用了一两年了，平时感觉还好，虽然小 bug 有点多。</p>\n<p>今天早上用着正常，合上盖子带来单位上班，突然发现无线鼠标不能用了，触摸板也不能用了。想着难道触摸板被关了？想打开控制中心看看，控制中心也打不开了。</p>\n<p>奇怪的是，有线鼠标还能用。</p>\n<p>突然就很想把开发环境切回 win10 了，不知道现在 wsl2 做开发怎么样，主要是 web 开发，flutter 开发。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1623991483, "replies": 51, "id": 784199}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1622572533", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1622572533", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 173513, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533", "stars": 3261, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "undefine2020", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2eeff017f78826fcfe1c71b36b3002f6?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/undefine2020", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1604540616, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2eeff017f78826fcfe1c71b36b3002f6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2eeff017f78826fcfe1c71b36b3002f6?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 516026}, "last_reply_by": "js9527", "last_touched": 1624004279, "title": "国外就没有类似 115 的给力离线下载神器吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/784123", "created": 1623978743, "content": "还是用国外的保险", "content_rendered": "<p>还是用国外的保险</p>\n", "last_modified": 1623978743, "replies": 49, "id": 784123}]